data.description: The perfect 3 bedroom 2 bath one story does exist! Beautiful open concept, vaulted ceilings in the spacious family room. Gas fireplace. Lovely master bedroom with trey ceiling and large walk in closet. Master bath complete with tile foors, dual vanity, large soaking tub and separate shower. Laundry/mud room just off garage. Split floorplan with  2 additional bedrooms and full bath on the opposite side of the home for privacy. Large kitchen with stainless steel appliances and plenty of counter/cabinet space. Breakfast nook with sliding glass door to the fully fenced backyard. Covered pergola make this the perfect place to kick back and relax. Storage shed is only a year old! Located in the heart of Jacksonville, with all of the shopping and restaurants just around the corner! Washer and dryer do convey. Just outside city limits
